description: <p>Ruda is a sans serif \
  typeface originally developed \
  for a specific context of use, product labels. \
  Designed by Mariela Monsalve and Angelina Snchez, \
  Ruda features a very large x-height, low cap-height \
  and open forms.</p> \
  <p>Ruda is a collaboration between \
  <a href="http://www.mukamonsalve.com.ar">marie monsalve</a> \
  and <a href="http://www.angelinasanchez.com.ar">Angelina \
  Sanchez</a>.</p>

